et non-linear ML\nmethods in (biomechanical) gait analysis and thereby supplies a powerful tool\nfor analysis, diagnosis and treatment of human gait.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 13 Aug 2018 16:04:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 Feb 2019 13:26:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-28"}
